The makefile takes as a parameter the name of the target test file. At the
moment, we have one test file ready:

To change number of asyncs, nodes, inputs look adjust values in the makefile.

To Build and Run:
(Note: Max Input Size is 37 Chapters)
make TARGET_CLASS=CharFrequency.x10
make TARGET_CLASS=WordCount.x10

make TARGET_CLASS=SumIntegers.x10
make TARGET_CLASS=DistributedSort.x10

